name: Terminal Finance CEO: Code Solves CEX Failures; DEX Raises $280M Pre-Launch
description: The Saint of Wet Porcelain weeps the dark fluid of broken trust, its heavy custody dissolved. A biomechanical architect collects the sorrow, rendering the failure into cyan-magenta logic. The lattice of sacred geometry affirms the code's resilience, ushering in the true ledger, eternal and unbound.
